snippet.title: The many different PERSONALITIES of Amber Heard. Amber Heard EXPOSED AGAIN!
snippet.description:
#AmberHeard #JusticeForJohnnyDepp
In this video I discuss the several personalities of Amber Heard. I believe Amber Heard has more than one personality. 
Disclaimer: I am not a personality expert, I just call what I see when I analyze Amber Heard's behavior. Amber is likely mentally ill in my opinion, but that should be left to the professionals to officially diagnose her.
